{"tid":155281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日一柒事","createTime":"2017-03-14T01:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T01:40:35.000Z","uid":89881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd7be475dfdcb5b65767cec73e5860bb67008de","tid":155281,"uid":89881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說今日我搭地鐵，好好彩有位坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐左落去之後就開始玩手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩到一半，抬頭見到好大既一個肚腩<br />\n咁我就即刻心諗 有大肚婆係面前 仲5係我表現愛心既好時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是就好有禮貌咁同佢講聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :小姐 你要唔要坐？<br />\n講完之後，果小姐呆左一呆，答<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :唔洗啦<br />\n<br />\n好啦咁，可能你下站落，所以唔洗坐。<br />\n點知，佢下站冇落到，之後聽到佢打電話同朋友講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我竟然肥到要人讓坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係柒到冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲打講下啲柒事 等我心理平衡下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}